text: Gabriel Roth may refer to: * Gabriel Roth (musician), American musician and producer * Gabriel Roth (footballer) (born 1979), Argentine association football player * Gabriel Roth (economist), writer on Transport economics * Gabriel Roth (filmmaker) (born 1974), brother and sometime collaborator of Eli Roth ==Similar spellings== * Gabriele Roth (born 1967) German hurdler * Gabrielle Roth (1941–2012), American dancer
